        },
        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:1:53:3",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/53/1069",
        "text": [
          " اَلصَّلاَةِ قَالَ «لاَ بَأْسَ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.1069 - Al-Halabi asked Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) about a person who scratches himself while in prayer. He (as) replied: \"There is no harm.\""
          ]
        }
      },
