        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:1:53:4",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/53/1070",
        "text": [
          " اَلصَّلاَةِ أَ يَنْقُضُ ذَلِكَ صَلاَتَهُ وَ وُضُوءَهُ قَالَ «لاَ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.1070 - He asked him about a person who kills a louse, a flea, a mosquito, or a fly while in prayer. Does this invalidate his prayer and wudu?\nImam (as) said: \"No.\""
          ]
        }
      },
      {
        "index": 1066,
        "local_index": 5,
        "narrator_chain": {
